<headline>Special Weather Statement issued December 31 at 6:29PM EST  by NWS Buffalo</headline>
<description>...Locally dense fog near Lake Ontario...
Some locally dense fog has formed over portions of Niagara,
Orleans, and Monroe counties this evening with reports of
visibilities near or under a quarter mile. If traveling across
routes 18, 104 or 31, be prepaired for rapidly changing
visibilities.</description>
